         <para/>
         <bibliography id="ch0011s0005bib0001">
            <bibliomixed id="ch0011s0005bib01">Halter Jordan, M. (2022). Varcarolis’ foundations of psychiatric-mental health nursing: A clinical approach (9th ed.). Elsevier.</bibliomixed>
